body: "Repository setup requirements:\n- Description and homepage should match package.json and README.\n- Issues should remain enabled for public support.\n- Wiki should remain disabled to keep documentation canonical in README and repo files.\n- GitHub Projects may be disabled if not needed because pm is the canonical project-management system.\n- No paid GitHub features are required or configured.\n- Visibility should match the package public-release posture after the secret-history audit is clean."
